{"PROUD":[{"def":"Feeling or manifesting pride, in a good or bad sense; as: (a) Possessing or showing too great self-esteem; overrating one's excellences; hence, arrogant; haughty; lordly; presumptuous.","pos":""},{"def":"Giving reason or occasion for pride or self-gratulation; worthy of admiration; grand; splendid; magnificent; admirable; ostentatious.","pos":""}],"PROUDLING":[{"def":"A proud or haughty person.","pos":""}],"PROUDLY":[{"def":"In a proud manner; with lofty airs or mien; haughtily; arrogantly; boastfully.","pos":""}],"PROUDNESS":[{"def":"The quality of being proud; pride.","pos":""}],"PROUSTITE":[{"def":"A sulphide of arsenic and silver of a beautiful cochineal-red color, occurring in rhombohedral crystals, and also massive; ruby silver.","pos":""}]}